

Usage:
Just put the /pp2data folder into this folder and run "taskN.py" (with python 3.5 or above).
For task3, run with "-v" to trace iteration.

Code structure:
/core/linreg.py: functions that trains the model using least square / MAP.
/core/metrics.py: functions that calculates MSE and data for plotting learning curve.
/utils/dataset.py: contains a function that draw random subset of specified size from the data set.
/task1(2,3,4).py: code for the corresponding Task.
